# Protocol Sketch

Jaringan pages are UTF-8, line-oriented, and mostly useful as plain text.

Supported blocks in the current prototype:

```plain
# Heading

Paragraph text.

=> about.jrg Link label
! action-id label="Button label" target="action-target"
@ ./image.png alt="Image alt text"
```

Network transport will use `jrg://host/path` later. M1 intentionally opens local `.jrg` files first.

=> hello.jrg Home
=> about.jrg About Jaringan
